astraiea.layer2

Class Layer2

  • java.lang.Object
    • astraiea.layer2.Layer2

  • public final class Layer2
extends java.lang.Object
    Layer2 organises the running of two or more metaheuristics. It then passes the results onto Layer1 for analysing.
    Author:
    Geoffrey Neumann, Jerry Swan
